---
import background1 from "../assets/bg1.webp";
import CrossDecorator from "./CrossDecorator.astro";
---

<section
  class="relative w-full h-[90vh] px-6 sm:px-16 md:px-20 lg:px-32 flex items-center"
  aria-label="Banner principal"
>
  <img
    src={background1.src}
    alt=""
    aria-hidden="true"
    width={1536}
    height={1024}
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-screen object-cover object-center hero-bg"
  />

  <div class="absolute inset-0 hero-overlay"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 pt-40 pb-6 sm:pt-36 sm:pb-10 md:py-28 md:mt-16">
    <div class="hero-enter">
      <CrossDecorator text="Centrados en la Palabra de Dios" />
    </div>
    <h1
      class="font-heading text-white text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl leading-[1.05] tracking-tight drop-shadow-md hero-enter"
      style="animation-delay: 150ms"
    >
      Iglesia Bautista<br />Reformada
    </h1>

    <p
      class="mt-7 font-serif italic text-white/75 text-lg sm:text-xl max-w-lg hero-enter"
      style="animation-delay: 350ms"
    >
      "Y aquel Verbo fue hecho carne, y habitó entre nosotros (y vimos su
      gloria, gloria como del unigénito del Padre), lleno de gracia y de
      verdad."
      <span
        class="block not-italic font-body text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mt-2 text-white/50"
      >
        — San Juan 1:12
      </span>
    </p>

    <div
      class="hidden sm:flex mt-10 flex-row gap-3 hero-enter"
      style="animation-delay: 550ms"
    >
      <a
        href="/horarios"
        class="px-7 py-3 bg-btn hover:bg-btn-hover text-white text-sm font-medium tracking-wide rounded transition-colors duration-200 text-center"
      >
        Nuestros Horarios
      </a>
      <a
        href="/quienes-somos"
        class="px-7 py-3 border btn-outline hover:border-white text-white text-sm font-medium tracking-wide rounded transition-colors duration-200 text-center"
      >
        Conócenos
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="absolute left-0 bottom-0 w-full overflow-hidden leading-none rotate-180"
  >
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      viewBox="0 0 1440 120"
      class="w-full h-12"
      preserveAspectRatio="none"
    >
      <path
        class="fill-primary"
        d="M0,80L80,90.7C160,101,320,123,480,106.7C640,91,800,37,960,26.7C1120,16,1280,48,1360,64L1440,80L1440,0L0,0Z"
      ></path>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>
